summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Unhinged dating app MVP. Fixed critical backend MongoDB ObjectId serialization bug and frontend routing issue. All core features now working perfectly including auth, profile setup, AI roast generation, and navigation.

critical_bugs.issue: MongoDB ObjectId serialization error causing 500 internal server error
critical_bugs.impact: Blocked all user registration and authentication
critical_bugs.status: FIXED - Modified registration endpoint to exclude _id field from MongoDB queries

ui_bugs.issue: Registration redirecting to discover instead of profile setup for incomplete profiles
ui_bugs.status: FIXED - Updated routing logic to check profile_complete status
